# Customised frame sizes will need to be updated to remain consistent with
their pre-update size!
# External modifications which use the [addon]:RegisterSize function will need
to be updated to remove that call as it is no longer needed. :RegisterFontSize
should still be used to scale fonts with the user option.

* improved graphical fidelity when fix aliasing is disabled
* frame sizes can now be changed without reloading the UI
* fix frame glow showing through faded frames

